germans drove them through hungary to the west in an exodus that 
helped trigger last falls democratic changes now the trabi 
seems more like an inescapable reminder of the past 
blank says the mood is hopeful after the conservative victory in 
east germanys free elections march 18 
the winning threeparty alliance heavily backed by the 
conservative bonn government has promised quick union with rich 
west germany 
