this has been a season in which many new shows 
gave bush league a bad name but miracles do occur like cbs 
bagdad cafe premiering tonight and a saturday preview of 
nbcs carol amp co 
cbs show a situation comedy costars whoopi goldberg and jean 
stapleton 
nbcs effort which will get a regular saturday slot is 
anthology comedy a series of different shows performed by carol 
burnett and a talented troupe 
each debut episode is excellent in its own way particularly 
carol amp co which has the different kind of look and feel a 
network needs to battle the diverse wares offered by the 
evergrowing cable tv monster 
