what kind of company is it that doesnt honor its contracts 
he asked 
price did not return a phone call to his office wednesday he 
retired as an employee on march 15 but the company is providing 
him office space and secretarial support under his consulting 
contract the proxy statement said he also remains chairman of the 
board 
