was part of a contract signed in 1986 when the company was faced 
with an arduous restructuring 
certainly over the life of these contracts the stockholders 
and bob would have liked to have seen better performance ryan 
said but having a contract that protects against the risks and 
takes into account the tasks before the individual the contracts 
do not seem inappropriate 
