amount equal to three times his final annual base pay of 873600 
and the amount of his accrued vacation according to the proxy 
statement 
he also was entitled to 163054 in annual supplemental pension 
but elected to receive the lump sum present value of the benefits 
1469932 upon his retirement the supplemental pension is above 
prices normal annual pension of 300000 ryan said 
