data common stock as of dec 31 1989 but the option price of 
2227 a share is above the stocks current trading price of 19 to 
20 a share making the options worthless 
but if the stock price rises substantially in the next year 
price would stand to get additional bonus money under the companys 
longterm performance incentive plan the proxy statement said 
